=== WEIGHT_BALANCE ===
# id: 58
# title: The Weight Balance
# chinese_title: 天平之谜
# category: Puzzle
# mode: dungeon

A large scale dominates the center of the room. Various objects line the shelves — each labeled with a Chinese character and a weight. The door ahead will only open when both sides of the scale are perfectly balanced. The trick lies in understanding which characters share radicals.

* [Balance the scale using radical groupings]
  ~ gain_radical("大")
  "平" (píng) — flat, balanced, peace
* [Weigh each object systematically]
  ~ gain_xp(20)
  "量" (liáng) — to measure, quantity
* [Guess and adjust until balanced]
  ~ gain_xp(10)
  "试" (shì) — to try, to attempt
